Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait - User when followed by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time between Accepted + In Progress and Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time from Accepted + Wait - User to Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - User compared to Accepted + Wait - Vendor
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - User compared to Accepted + Wait - Implementation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that do not contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Total time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum time from Accepted + Wait - User to Completed + Resolved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User when preceded by Accepted + Assigned
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait - User in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time between consecutive occurrences of Accepted + Wait - User within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait - User to the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants where Completed + In Call appears before it
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that transition directly to Completed + Resolved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - User compared to the overall average activity time in VINST logs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Total time from case start to Accepted + Wait - User in cases that eventually execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User when it occurs after a second Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Time elapsed between Accepted + Wait - User and the final resolution (Completed + Closed) in complex multi-loop variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Closed'
